{"tid":135842,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"墾丁兩日一夜","createTime":"2017-02-26T15:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T17:02:09.000Z","uid":28540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe721744bfc313a2867ec36d150b69122460a35d","tid":135842,"uid":28540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"墾丁兩日一夜 夠唔夠玩 第二日大約晏就四點出高雄到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40508a49f200972d79e63e3c5efac92d4a865c9","tid":135842,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"去下個海洋國立博物館同埋風吹沙，玩下水上活動同埋行下條大街"},{"pid":"eac8df14edd23c54a95ab22e91a79577724fd1a1","tid":135842,"uid":83322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"揸下電單車去放煙花，冬天唔落水就夠玩啦"},{"pid":"1c9e020fc1a5611ea9c966b18848071f0d55a4cd","tid":135842,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"如果想感受下一份寧靜<br />\n睇下星(天氣既野)<br />\n不妨多留一晚"},{"pid":"4bfac09ee162d64be7113da59e708158610f683c","tid":135842,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"一定唔夠啦"},{"pid":"049fd5e183b213132b4419f74b680238085aaa4c","tid":135842,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:42:58.000Z","msg":"墾丁俾我玩7日都願，當俾自己靜下"},{"pid":"fa8673392acfbeb3e2aeb851d3dd680d87290407","tid":135842,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:54:13.000Z","msg":"你想慢遊嘅可以加多日嘅<br />\n暑假去咗墾丁留咗五日 落咗兩日雨<br />\n令到我覺得墾丁好悶 因為一落雨好似真係得返海生館去到咁 我地仲去埋啤酒博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後出火個啲又冇乜嘢睇 同埋而家好似唔比放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f0c32b4d542b0de751762b05076ba258cb1235","tid":135842,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"俾我會選擇3日"},{"pid":"a905ad4c6537b73edad3629d8719c6416e8355bf","tid":135842,"uid":87397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"三日兩夜會好啲 無咁趕<br />\n玩水都無左大半日"},{"pid":"1c7c9d94bf4dc916f107c3b21c0556795f324a42","tid":135842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:39:32.000Z","msg":"訓一晚你不如唔好去"},{"pid":"c6bde8a77bce6031d10bd29b8bbe4157549458c5","tid":135842,"uid":28540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"台南三日兩夜<br />\n墾丁三日兩夜<br />\n高雄兩日一夜<br />\n<br />\n晚機7點幾返 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a5e4818a7dbdb1da88e04b6e445bbd188206ad","tid":135842,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓一晚你不如唔好去</blockquote><br />\n唔落水都OK嘅，落水得一晚就真係慳返唔好去好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，三日兩夜都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f84f79505d2cda37a29289f5fa1f1b02d6c36b","tid":135842,"uid":28540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台南三日兩夜<br />\n墾丁三日兩夜<br />\n高雄兩日一夜<br />\n<br />\n晚機7點幾返 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f389b2eb51003c3128db2a88b2431663f868be","tid":135842,"uid":28540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo